\ Cross-system seam torture, part 2 of 2: load the image built by 133 in a
\ fresh process and prove every seam survived the round-trip and a GC.
"/tmp/lf-torture.image" load-image
gc
prod . cr                                       \ 42   fused superword
5 poly . cr                                     \ 11   locals + inlined call
4 sumto . cr                                    \ 10   recursion + branch
V $ . cr                                        \ 99   bound logic var
P reify . cr                                    \ [( 5 5 null )]   shared var preserved
REL { :role :wizard } query size . cr           \ 1    relation query
REL { :role :wizard } query 0 @i :name @ . cr    \ :gandalf   row content
5 K resume . cr                                 \ 10   continuation resumed cross-process
M . cr                                          \ the 2x2 matrix
[: [ 0 0 0 0 ] drop :] 2000 times  gc            \ post-load GC ...
prod . cr                                       \ 42   ... dispatch still works
bye
